1
00:00:06,570 --> 00:00:11,950
♪Obsessions penned
into an everlasting love♪

2
00:00:12,330 --> 00:00:17,580
♪Affections gently linger
around fingertips♪

3
00:00:17,640 --> 00:00:23,140
♪May stars guide us through rough waves♪

4
00:00:23,420 --> 00:00:28,520
♪I give all my love unreservedly♪

5
00:00:29,030 --> 00:00:30,900
♪May transient frost♪

6
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,690
♪Persist through obstacles for love♪

7
00:00:34,820 --> 00:00:40,330
♪I wait for you to look back
in this rocky life♪

8
00:00:40,650 --> 00:00:42,550
♪I can stay for the promise♪

9
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:46,180
♪Despite seasons recur♪

10
00:00:46,380 --> 00:00:51,760
♪The love deep within
will transcend time♪

11
00:00:51,760 --> 00:00:57,500
[Secrets of the Shadow Sect]

12
00:00:57,540 --> 00:01:00,820
[Episode 16]

13
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:11,500
I was wondering about
the identity of the man

14
00:01:11,500 --> 00:01:12,940
that Xuan drew on this fan.

15
00:01:13,380 --> 00:01:14,780
It turns out to be him.

16
00:01:16,660 --> 00:01:17,460
Jing.

17
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:18,660
Young Master.

18
00:01:18,900 --> 00:01:20,540
Look into that Yingshi

19
00:01:20,820 --> 00:01:21,700
beside Xuan.

20
00:01:21,980 --> 00:01:23,420
Find everything about him.

21
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:25,620
Xuan is suspicious.

22
00:01:25,620 --> 00:01:27,180
She never trusts anyone easily.

23
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:28,300
There must be

24
00:01:28,300 --> 00:01:29,860
a reason

25
00:01:30,100 --> 00:01:31,420
why he could win her trust.

26
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:32,900
Yes.

27
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:35,020
Also,

28
00:01:35,500 --> 00:01:37,420
inform the Medicine King Valley
to speed up.

29
00:01:37,740 --> 00:01:38,740
Otherwise,

30
00:01:39,300 --> 00:01:41,420
things would get out of control.

31
00:01:42,260 --> 00:01:43,420
I will send them a message now.

32
00:01:46,220 --> 00:01:48,020
Medicine King Valley sent word

33
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:51,180
saying they want shadow guards
for blood slaves.

34
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:53,860
Yingshi.

35
00:01:57,070 --> 00:02:01,170
[Xuantian House]

36
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:15,500
What's so special about this hairpin?

37
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:17,060
You cherish it dearly

38
00:02:17,060 --> 00:02:18,140
and won't stop looking at it.

39
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:19,940
Could it be

40
00:02:19,940 --> 00:02:20,980
a gift from Yingshi?

41
00:02:21,980 --> 00:02:22,820
Brat.

42
00:02:22,820 --> 00:02:23,700
Nonsense.

43
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:24,740
Fine.

44
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:25,860
Look at your shy face.

45
00:02:25,860 --> 00:02:27,260
I won't tease you anymore.

46
00:02:27,300 --> 00:02:28,660
But this hairpin

47
00:02:28,740 --> 00:02:29,500
looks like

48
00:02:29,500 --> 00:02:30,860
a lot of work.

49
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:33,740
I know, right?

50
00:02:49,260 --> 00:02:51,100
The drug Ling Yuanzheng used

51
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,700
should be this one.

52
00:02:56,060 --> 00:02:57,260
Previously,

53
00:02:57,380 --> 00:02:59,380
I tested it on death warriors.

54
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:00,660
The Soul-shattering Pill

55
00:03:00,820 --> 00:03:02,900
didn't take effect on them that month.

56
00:03:11,340 --> 00:03:12,420
So now,

57
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,060
we only need the leading ingredient.

58
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,500
That's to obtain his blood.

59
00:03:18,060 --> 00:03:19,860
And so, the danger
of the Shadow Sect

60
00:03:19,860 --> 00:03:21,020
can be resolved.

61
00:03:49,660 --> 00:03:50,780
Xuan.

62
00:03:52,740 --> 00:03:54,260
You are here.

63
00:03:56,620 --> 00:03:58,500
You seem very happy to see me.

64
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:00,980
I ruled

65
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:03,260
the Lingtian Palace for years.

66
00:04:04,300 --> 00:04:06,980
Do you think I have no backup plan?

67
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:10,180
You are my daughter

68
00:04:10,740 --> 00:04:13,300
and the young master
of the Lingtian Palace.

69
00:04:13,620 --> 00:04:14,980
You will take over this place

70
00:04:15,460 --> 00:04:17,300
sooner or later.

71
00:04:18,940 --> 00:04:20,460
I can

72
00:04:21,300 --> 00:04:23,340
give you

73
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:26,060
the formula of the Soul-shattering Pill.

74
00:04:28,180 --> 00:04:29,460
What a shame.

75
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:31,380
You are going to be disappointed.

76
00:04:31,660 --> 00:04:33,300
I have already found the formula.

77
00:04:36,940 --> 00:04:38,140
Impossible.

78
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:45,660
There is one thing

79
00:04:46,460 --> 00:04:48,340
you might not know, Father.

80
00:04:49,540 --> 00:04:51,820
Actually, Mr. Ya comes
from a medical sect.

81
00:04:52,740 --> 00:04:53,700
He has already

82
00:04:54,180 --> 00:04:55,220
developed

83
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:56,940
the antidote
to the Soul-shattering Pill.

84
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:00,340
What did you say?

85
00:05:02,220 --> 00:05:03,300
I heard

86
00:05:03,900 --> 00:05:05,460
that this drug was spread
to the martial arts world

87
00:05:05,460 --> 00:05:06,820
through the Medicine King Valley

88
00:05:07,060 --> 00:05:08,580
to save lives.

89
00:05:09,180 --> 00:05:10,540
But when it fell into your hands...

90
00:05:14,460 --> 00:05:15,580
Ling Yuanzheng.

91
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:18,020
I've seen through your plan long ago.

92
00:05:19,460 --> 00:05:21,100
I often wondered

93
00:05:21,980 --> 00:05:23,380
why a selfish and cold person
like you

94
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:25,020
would exist in this world.

95
00:05:25,780 --> 00:05:28,380
Lingtian Palace is the lifework
of our ancestors.

96
00:05:30,020 --> 00:05:31,060
I won't allow you

97
00:05:31,700 --> 00:05:33,580
to use it
to destroy the martial arts world.

98
00:05:35,540 --> 00:05:36,900
If you truly feel sorry,

99
00:05:37,780 --> 00:05:39,420
release all members from other sects.

100
00:05:41,140 --> 00:05:43,180
Once the shadow guards are detoxified,

101
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:45,180
I will release you

102
00:05:46,220 --> 00:05:48,180
and send you to Lingyin Peak
to live out your days.

103
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,420
You won't find them.

104
00:05:54,020 --> 00:05:54,820
Xuan.

105
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:56,740
You are my child.

106
00:05:57,820 --> 00:05:59,180
The blood flowing in you

107
00:05:59,500 --> 00:06:01,540
is the same as mine.

108
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:03,180
I admit it.

109
00:06:04,140 --> 00:06:06,540
I wanted something from your mother

110
00:06:07,660 --> 00:06:09,580
and deceived her into marrying me
for years.

111
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:12,900
But what about you?

112
00:06:13,940 --> 00:06:15,900
Haven't you been playing

113
00:06:16,220 --> 00:06:18,740
the obedient daughter in front of me
for many years?

114
00:06:19,140 --> 00:06:21,300
You are no different from me.

115
00:06:21,580 --> 00:06:22,660
You are no better

116
00:06:23,180 --> 00:06:24,820
than me!

117
00:06:24,820 --> 00:06:25,980
Don't you mention my mother!

118
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:27,820
I'm not like you.

119
00:06:29,100 --> 00:06:31,540
I will never become a despicable person
like you.

120
00:06:32,100 --> 00:06:34,180
I look forward to that.

121
00:06:34,740 --> 00:06:36,700
I will persist

122
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,460
and see

123
00:06:38,820 --> 00:06:40,900
how you choose
when the very moment comes.

124
00:07:05,060 --> 00:07:05,860
Master.

125
00:07:06,180 --> 00:07:07,140
Stay still.

126
00:07:07,540 --> 00:07:08,700
Let me lean on you.

127
00:07:14,620 --> 00:07:16,540
Did anything happen in the dungeon?

128
00:07:20,460 --> 00:07:21,620
He said

129
00:07:22,380 --> 00:07:24,220
the blood flowing in me
is the same as his

130
00:07:25,340 --> 00:07:27,220
and I will end up like him.

131
00:07:36,460 --> 00:07:38,580
The former Master Ling has a way
of manipulating people's minds.

132
00:07:38,940 --> 00:07:40,460
He knew what you care about.

133
00:07:40,660 --> 00:07:42,180
That's why he was provoking you.

134
00:07:43,300 --> 00:07:44,340
You and him

135
00:07:44,780 --> 00:07:46,100
are different.

136
00:07:47,220 --> 00:07:48,020
Oh?

137
00:07:48,860 --> 00:07:50,220
You never thought about

138
00:07:50,220 --> 00:07:51,580
using drugs to control the Shadow Sect.

139
00:07:52,020 --> 00:07:53,140
So you tried everything you could

140
00:07:53,140 --> 00:07:54,700
to detoxify all the shadow guards.

141
00:07:54,740 --> 00:07:55,580
Didn't you?

142
00:07:57,860 --> 00:07:59,980
But I'm using that on you.

143
00:08:01,780 --> 00:08:02,940
It's different for me.

144
00:08:04,780 --> 00:08:05,940
How is it different?

145
00:08:07,940 --> 00:08:08,660
I

146
00:08:09,300 --> 00:08:10,580
took it willingly.

147
00:08:12,820 --> 00:08:14,020
- Master Ling!
- Master Ling!

148
00:08:14,020 --> 00:08:14,980
Something has happened!

149
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:23,260
♪If hand waves are
the prelude to farewell♪

150
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:26,860
♪If words hold no intention to stall♪

151
00:08:27,420 --> 00:08:29,140
♪Goodbye♪

152
00:08:29,340 --> 00:08:33,180
♪Should be reserved
for when our lives are at stake♪

153
00:08:34,460 --> 00:08:37,790
♪If time rushes swiftly
like wind and dust♪

154
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:41,500
♪If tears come before words
after waking up♪

155
00:08:41,900 --> 00:08:44,180
♪May you not be drowned in bitterness♪

156
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:45,780
♪I only wish your eyes♪

157
00:08:45,920 --> 00:08:48,840
♪As pure as snow♪
